## 六、自审命令

```bash
# L4：跨 Context 直接导入检测
grep -rn "from app.services.user" backend/app/services/diagnosis/ && echo "FAIL: cross-context import" || echo "PASS"

# L4：Domain Event 命名规范
grep -rn "Event\s*=" backend/app/contexts/ | grep -v "Event\s*=\s*\"[A-Z][a-zA-Z]*Event\"" && echo "FAIL: bad event name" || echo "PASS"

# L4：禁止跨 Context 共享数据库表
grep -rn "from app.contexts.user.infrastructure" backend/app/contexts/diagnosis/ && echo "FAIL: cross-context DB access" || echo "PASS"
```

